Hyperion, the Amiga's premier entertainment software company, has acquired a
license from Activision Inc. (NASDAQ: AVTI) to port Ritual's critically
acclaimed ego-shooter "SiN" to the Amiga and Linux platforms. SiN is based on ID
Software's spectacular Quake 2 engine using OpenGL.

