versions by the end of Q2 2000. SiN is synonymous with first rate, unadulterated
action with relatively low system requirements so Amiga and Linux users have
something to look forward to."

The Amiga version will require a PPC (supported through WarpOS) and will support
3D accelerators through Warp3D and Hyperion's custom OpenGL implementation
(MiniGL).

